ws-camerad (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * High-performance multi-consumer camera daemon
  * V4L2 M2M hardware H.264 encoding
  * GStreamer RTSP streaming server
  * Shared memory frame distribution (YUV420/BGR)
  * Ring buffer for pre-event clip recording
  * Still capture with JPEG compression
  * Unix socket control interface

